<view class="page">
  <view class="header-card">
    <view class="hero-kicker">CREATIVE CONTROL PANEL</view>
    <view class="hero-top">
      <view class="page-title">创作互动管理</view>
      <view class="header-status {{syncing ? 'is-loading' : 'is-ready'}}">{{syncing ? '同步中' : '已同步'}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="page-desc">这里集中放置创作互动玩法的后台入口，当前已接入双盲作诗与诗词摊煎饼两条管理链路。</view>
    <view class="hero-meta-row">
      <view class="hero-meta-pill" wx:if="{{blindPoemManageVisible}}">双盲作诗</view>
      <view class="hero-meta-pill" wx:if="{{poemPancakeManageVisible}}">诗词摊煎饼</view>
      <view class="hero-meta-pill">后台表单配置</view>
    </view>
    <view class="sync-tip" wx:if="{{syncing}}">权限信息正在静默刷新，你可以先进入当前可见模块。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-card error-card" wx:if="{{errorMessage && !hasContent}}">
    <view class="page-title">加载失败</view>
    <view class="page-desc">{{errorMessage}}</view>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="section-card clickable-card" wx:if="{{blindPoemManageVisible}}" bindtap="goBlindPoemManage">
      <view class="entry-card-row">
        <view class="entry-card-main">
          <view class="section-title">双盲作诗管理</view>
          <view class="entry-card-desc">管理模式启停、题库、作品审核与精选作品。</view>
        </view>
        <view class="entry-card-arrow">></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card clickable-card" wx:if="{{poemPancakeManageVisible}}" bindtap="goPoemPancakeManage">
      <view class="entry-card-row">
        <view class="entry-card-main">
          <view class="section-title">诗词摊煎饼管理</view>
          <view class="entry-card-desc">管理主题、活动时间、状态切换与当前共创进度。</view>
        </view>
        <view class="entry-card-arrow">></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
